{"tid":1634100,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知我地既優勢係咩？","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:38:03.000Z","uid":163639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b1a943bd277e890ac14ef861044da99257bbf6","tid":1634100,"uid":163639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"係網絡文宣呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地係掌握網絡既一代！<br />\n唔係班平均50歲up組成既政府！<br />\n<br />\n點解對家要搞lennon wall？<br />\n點解要搞商場唱歌？<br />\n點解要搞連登，想網禁？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地真係好驚，民心歸向，係拆不散</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n美國打中東搶石油，都會講到對方邪惡軸心甘，論武裝，美國一早贏晒，點解都要玩輿論戰？<br />\n<br />\n而家係2019呀！真正既戰場係心理上，點樣可以令一個政權倒下？就係連對家既人信心都開始動搖。<br />\n<br />\n你睇獅鳥既成功，每一次懷疑都係一次文宣好機會，證明前線唔係亂9甘黎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">100%信任前線，但唔代表信完就坐係度，而係要幫佢地拆，揾原因。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你估真係好撚多死忠藍絲咩？唔係叫佢地轉政見，係動搖呀！<br />\n<br />\n佢地好清楚咩叫先撩者賤，打死無怨。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">所以唔好再講裝修唔裝修，試著說點解要裝修？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1WcNx2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1WcNx2.jpg&h=f2d86be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V52vzc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV52vzc3.jpg&h=f163a64a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPf1FS5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPf1FS5.jpg&h=092554f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTPt5jM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTPt5jM.jpg&h=09afffcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y78q7x7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY78q7x7.jpg&h=c53c0453&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ea4d25adb5a506a00567b0eb31b0c3befd3ddb2","tid":1634100,"uid":163639,"like":0,"disli